{"title":"Enfermedades glomerulares","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Nefrología/Enfermedades glomerulares-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Enfermedades\\Nglomerulares","guid":"cPa4GiwpuifWtNFXhwCWjw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Terminología de enfermedades glomerulares.","guid":"Qry7HsFN4np_7BB_BTZ76g","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Primario","guid":"zj_ijCjjphRrrPrIiMD26Q","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"una enfermedad renal que afecta específicamente a los glomérulos\\N(p. ej., glomerulonefritis de cambios mínimos )","guid":"3nCPGyrsIeavemYV-2V2Lw","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Secundaria","guid":"HLOQn5Mw_Th1g7FLiHY50g","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"una enfermedad que afecta a los glomérulos en el contexto de una enfermedad sistémica (p. ej.,\\Nnefritis lúpica en el LES ) o una enfermedad que afecta a otro órgano (p. ej., nefropatía diabética )","guid":"DnhudKy6cxkh4us4CtGBzg","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"Difusa","guid":"8r4AbVCpvXa219r_lpa92w","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"> 50% de los glomérulos afectados (p. ej.,\\Nglomerulonefritis proliferativa difusa )","guid":"_EckUV1xb6Ta3ZNqYPMw1Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"Focal","guid":"Irikt9OYCgBszIih9ITXeA","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"< 50% de los glomérulos afectados (p. ej.,\\Nglomeruloesclerosis focal y segmentaria )","guid":"SOyPBV3OctS2YeGyecOvkg","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"1","text":"Global","guid":"D77q8Jp_oq3KbHVIUEeuvw","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"todo el glomérulo está afectado","guid":"sbS0wC2Nu33vdiI-U4pkGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"1","text":"Segmentario","guid":"a3xq9lhyfKsRkUQ0y_vu3w","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"sólo se afecta una parte del glomérulo .","guid":"dP4mxIb7jgKrvjyZIwvseA","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"1","text":"Proliferativo","guid":"ySXIpABlsz-0StnZK12dLA","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"un mayor número de células en el glomérulo .","guid":"SRzKhhxY1JT6F4hkhm2aOg","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"1","text":"Membranosa","guid":"05tjEt32ofELyfucV0Se2w","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"engrosamiento de la membrana basal glomerular\\N(p. ej., nefropatía membranosa )","guid":"uhalV1zT345t4BCyX-8wGg","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"1","text":"Esclerosante","guid":"wR7QB_Zfi9n5Tf8rtwXclQ","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"cicatrización del glomérulo .","guid":"cwetKbgmqyjMM-qBP6goMQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"1","text":"Necrosante ","guid":"AddU_mLFfQq6k149D72ffQ","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"muerte celular dentro del glomérulo","guid":"T9QFm5jJBl1qau-hntQ-6A","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"1","text":"Crescéntico","guid":"wcSMYs9zgmJ3iRgFajIYzQ","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"acumulación de células como macrófagos , fibroblastos\\Ny células epiteliales en el espacio de Bowman.","guid":"hcIZpRx8qD2e_IHW2eW0vw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"La barrera de filtración\\Nglomerular consta de 3 partes.","guid":"vuiIjIkffZ7obK_o270p_A","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Segmento inicial: el endotelio capilar glomerular\\Nfenestrado impide el paso de proteínas grandes .","guid":"6YyXejv_VETz9OEvZc5pvg","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Segundo segmento: La membrana basal glomerular ( MBG )\\Ncontiene una carga negativa producida por el sulfato de heparán .","guid":"56UJyssZmKBfXIWeQtenQA","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"Segmento final: las células epiteliales viscerales producen/mantienen la GBM y contienen\\Nuniones intercelulares creadas por podocitos que evitan una mayor pérdida de proteínas.","guid":"0PmpychaWdT5q40xHml1lg","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"25","text":"Daño a los glomérulos → alteración de la barrera de filtración glomerular → puede provocar síndrome nefrítico o nefrótico","guid":"143lEFMV_vhaRyRvzwcP-Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"Resumen de enfermedades\\Nglomerulares","guid":"7UPCEBL-krHC6liSUCgFDQ","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"Síndrome nefrótico\\Nversus nefrítico [1] [2]","guid":"T4K-HxUD_TYL0QsRO6DhSw","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"El síndrome nefrítico y el síndrome nefrótico son manifestaciones\\Nclínicas comunes de las enfermedades glomerulares .","guid":"vOpnIHDQpyMtTu9jQRnL4g","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"Ambos síndromes se componen de hallazgos clínicos característicos (p. ej., edema , hipertensión ) y de\\Nlaboratorio (p. ej., hematuria glomerular , proteinuria masiva ), que resultan del daño a los glomérulos .","guid":"x60k88dAPsu3nHKsuEblxw","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"31","text":"Las enfermedades glomerulares generalmente se clasifican\\Nsegún el síndrome que causan, que es nefrítico o nefrótico.","guid":"oGNlcE4npMjv-ncNe2XeSg","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"Algunas enfermedades que se manifiestan con síndrome nefrítico pueden causar simultáneamente\\Nproteinuria en rango nefrótico ( > 3,5 g/día ), la característica principal del síndrome nefrótico . Cuando se\\Ncumplen los criterios de ambos síndromes, los hallazgos se denominan síndrome mixto nefrítico-nefrótico .","guid":"COJz-sSIvI8GNisaCApyTQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"Clasificar la presentación del paciente como nefrítica, nefrótica o mixta nefrítico-nefrótica\\Npuede ayudar a reducir la lista de probables diagnósticos diferenciales.","guid":"mQUfEIFReFHuruQhUeAFsQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"31","text":"síndrome\\Nnefrítico","guid":"z-2ry_u25hwZMSu72I69dg","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"Presentación","guid":"FuRp4S-mSutqSwKC6bV4FQ","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"Proteinuria (< 3,5 g/día) (puede estar en rango nefrótico en casos graves) )","guid":"Il4qxM2va73uAYCIc9WTuQ","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"Hematuria con acantocitos","guid":"qi-ZS0PKEPiNkj9u5oFvhg","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"39","text":"Cilindros de glóbulos rojos en la orina","guid":"ud71ClMoD8hz9gESJNTBag","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"39","text":"Edema leve a moderado","guid":"IEE_ckSVqCgp7plI7rXELg","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"39","text":"Oliguria","guid":"t0AUXhp3ZXxbofrGS4gnHQ","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"39","text":"Azotemia","guid":"jb8nGxW7FcBjG4YQS07A7A","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"39","text":"Hipertensión","guid":"h0tr5xJoxDthJWHvQyLmhg","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"39","text":"Piuria estéril","guid":"XvM3ww4Ki_62jXjecIt6cQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"38","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"sfnbt0ZRng_29klEsPnsCA","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"Respuesta inflamatoria dentro de los glomérulos → alteración de la MBG → pérdida de glóbulos rojos excretados por\\Nvía renal ( acantocitos ) y ↓ TFG → hematuria , oliguria , azotemia y ↑ renina → edema e hipertensión","guid":"bu420e4TCBc7h1vkr0vHTQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"38","text":"Causas","guid":"ulU_dDpgNzFiR_QGdh3PcQ","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"Glomerulonefritis posestreptocócica","guid":"ztnl3Un7ejS9HZOlLZHOMA","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"Nefropatía por IgA ( enfermedad de Berger )","guid":"PitMUX9ntFundzypZC263w","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"Granulomatosis con poliangeítis","guid":"vk1JrSKYe3uQZZizEGYClA","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"50","text":"Poliangeítis microscópica","guid":"tuPeCZzJIwz0zKEyrjo8hw","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"50","text":"Granulomatosis eosinofílica con poliangeítis","guid":"uIYdLdv50yxl2VKP1KMiUg","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"50","text":"Síndrome de Goodpasture ( enfermedad anti- GBM )","guid":"7OQrjokrkUko0HkL0wstzw","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"50","text":"Síndrome de Alport ( nefritis hereditaria )","guid":"vlJTWZd_lvwH_7d14FMXUQ","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"50","text":"Enfermedad de la membrana basal delgada","guid":"EAU_32z5dZ-Z-4JIgECX1g","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"50","text":"Glomerulonefritis rápidamente progresiva ( RPGN )","guid":"1op34UU-BJ30cNV3KmQBRw","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"50","text":"nefritis lúpica","guid":"3HRDIJ1HHu_kIzVTQiW8gg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"31","text":"Síndrome\\Nnefrótico","guid":"cVyxfaXASrEzeY8JQs2-NQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"Presentación ","guid":"sjWfeH8JxxiYnWajvUAA7A","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"Proteinuria intensa (> 3,5 g/día)","guid":"mAamzrOYhJ_p-4y98ysSWg","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"hipoalbuminemia","guid":"Wzq_jhGSoq48cly1LxdoaQ","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"62","text":"Edema generalizado","guid":"N8-2pg5XGCzMCLcNc1tgGA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"62","text":"Hiperlipidemia y cilindros grasos en la orina →orina espumosa","guid":"k3tVqslf6QmidCaFbCH-MA","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"62","text":"Hipertensión","guid":"K-4T31_55DL-H7nhJI25Hw","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"62","text":"↑ Riesgo de tromboembolismo : (vía pérdida de antitrombina III )","guid":"9GvHOXdcjoCs1K63yPsa0w","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"62","text":"↑ Riesgo de infección (a través de pérdida de IgG y edema tisular que compromete el suministro de sangre local y la respuesta inmune )","guid":"wTI6UWRPJgeB4USWW5CoLg","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"61","text":"Fisiopatologia","guid":"c1bgdmw3m3ejGJQtt240Hg","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"Daño a los podocitos → daño estructural de la barrera de\\Nfiltración glomerular → pérdida renal masiva de proteínas","guid":"5O-wzojR2H7ihGHyPbAOBA","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"61","text":"Causas más comunes del\\Nsíndrome nefrítico-nefrótico :","guid":"g2W5aCBXSjDg-dVfxJOAng","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Glomerulonefritis membranoproliferativa","guid":"_DmvbrVKQqtQBn_x80G9qQ","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Glomerulonefritis proliferativa difusa","guid":"dh4d-Rh9Lybeg3Vv1k4unA","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"61","text":"Causa ","guid":"CGh4eWpHsjAxDf9I1fOuFg","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Debido al daño primario o\\Nsecundario de los podocitos.","guid":"QcMa6nJ0kbwDvhZ902p3PA","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"Enfermedad de cambios mínimos","guid":"FNac70HiCFYs-to9a9X_ww","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"Glomeruloesclerosis focal y segmentaria","guid":"3UU8OVsioPpfKyL5-cd3vQ","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"Nefropatía membranosa","guid":"J53E2JCDuJcgt5agF0Cazg","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"75","text":"Debido al daño secundario\\Nde los podocitos.","guid":"7qPSiTWQutcxW-U5w5CFog","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Nefropatía diabética","guid":"dOq1AB-Yfr6ZSD4Jq1Rsuw","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"Amiloidosis de cadenas ligeras de amiloide (AL) ,\\Nenfermedad por depósito de cadenas ligeras","guid":"SLKr2oG-cQif1ozNWYJTCg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"nefritis lúpica","guid":"avrCTAgmamfwChRVJp3JWA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"31","text":"Todas las enfermedades glomerulares pueden\\Nprovocar insuficiencia renal aguda y crónica .","guid":"v37DZRjT7tJQf7pgQsGV1A","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":84,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Nefrología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Nefrología","filename":"Enfermedades glomerulares-2024-1","id":"map_1309","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Enfermedades glomerulares-2024-1"}